QuestData.Title: Plunging Into Zul'Gurub
QuestData.Description: Zanzil the Outcast has once again escaped through one of his portals. Follow him!
QuestData.LogDescription: Pass through Zanzil's Portal.$b$bIf you become lost or need to return to Zul'Gurub, speak with Chabal at Hardwrench Hideaway.
QuestData.RewardText: You find yourself deeper within Zul'Gurub. The snake statues indicate that you have reached the terrace of High Priest Venoxis - follower of Hethiss, the snake god.
